metadata.name: Empepes - Evolutions (AI Animation) #1
metadata.description: Empeperors - Evolutions are a collection of 2000 AI animated NFTs, consisting of 226 unique editions, with each of the 34755 frames created by AI and acts as a free mint pass for the first ever 10k AI generative pfp collection coming up. A mix of animated art and animated pfps (will be separate collections later with 100% of primary sales and secondary royalties from it going to the holders), forms this evolved generation of Empeperors. CC0.
